*Policajci su dolazili redovno da obezbede okolinu. (The police officers were coming regularly to secure the environment.)

*Oni su poštovali policajce koji su se trudili da budu profesionalni. (They respected the police officers who were trying to be professional.)

*U gradu je bilo puno policajaca koji su hodali ulicama. (There were a lot of police officers walking the streets in the city.)

*Dok su policajci bili zauzeti, lopovi su pokušali da pobegnu. (While the police officers were busy, the thieves tried to escape.)

*Oni su zaustavili policajca da ih izvede iz zamke. (They stopped a police officer to lead them out of the trap.)

*Mnogi policajci su bili ranjeni u sukobima. (Many police officers were wounded in the clashes.)